high_descs: Turn left and walk into the other room and go to the coffee table.
Pick up the blue vase from the coffee table.
Turn right and walk in front of the floor lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a blue vase by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the middle of the room, the turn right again and approach the coffee table then turn left to face it.
Take the blue decoration off of the right edge of the table.
Turn to the right, then turn to the right again and face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: To see the decoration in the light.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, then turn right and walk to the coffee table in the living room
Pick up the blue vase from the coffee table
Turn right and walk up to the floor lamp in the corner by the couch
anns.task_desc: Look at the blue vase under the light of the floor lamp
